Title: Not A Murder Story
Summary: A series of bizarre events unfold in a community after an odd murder case is discovered. The residents all have connections with the victim and hidden secrets. After a night of passion with his neighbor Lin Mei (Sonia Sui), Dongdong (Kuan-ting Liu) finds her dead. He must hide his presence at the scene while trying to find the true killer, but uncovers more secrets than he bargained for.
